    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Plate armor pieces for the left hand and arm, protecting the hand and forearm up to or slightly beyond the elbow. They were used from the 15th through the 17th century, particularly in jousts.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
